content: अनीश्वर {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Having no superior, uncontrolled. {@--2@} Unable; शयिता सविधेप्यनीश्वरा सफलीकर्तुमहो मनोरथान् <ls>Bv. 2. 182.</ls> {@--3@} Not relating to God; ध्यानेनानीश्वरान् गुणान्-दहेत् <ls>Ms. 6. 72.</ls> {@--4@} Not acknowledging God, atheistical. --रं The godless one (with Sāṃkhyas), epithet of the world; जगदाहुरनीश्वरम्.
